# Archive Folder Structure

This folder contains your document archive organized by categories:

- academic/     - Degrees, transcripts, diplomas
- identity/     - Passports, IDs, licenses
- finance/      - Tax returns, statements, investments
- family/       - Family photos, documents
- property/     - Deeds, registrations
- medical/      - Health records, insurance
- certificates/ - Professional certifications
- receipts/     - Purchase receipts, bills
- personal/     - Personal documents, journals

Place your files in the appropriate category folders and update
the data/archive-manifest.json file to register them in the app.
